" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-cont=
ainer-id=3D"1707781098" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"41" alt=
=3D"" width=3D"468" height=3D"432"></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-03.SD:TransactionDetails(CustomerPortal)-SecurityAspects">Secu=
rity Aspects</h2>
<p>The Galaxy application security is per below.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Authentication</strong>: It will be handled with Ping Federate =
using PKCE flow.</li>
<li><strong>Authorisation</strong>: &nbsp;The authenticated user is entitle=
d to see the transaction details for any of the accounts stored in the Mesh=
 secrets (tactical solutions).</li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"id-03.SD:TransactionDetails(CustomerPortal)-ErrorHandling">Error =
Handling</h2>
<p><strong>Summary</strong></p>
<p>For Release, the below error codes should be handled by the UI:</p>
<ul>
<li>Bad Request Error</li>
<li>Server Error</li>
<li>Timeout Error</li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"id-03.SD:TransactionDetails(CustomerPortal)-Data&amp;InformationM=
odel">Data &amp; Information Model&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>
<ul>
<li><span>Transactions listing UI-Experience API Mapping:<span> <a href=3D"=
/display/ARTC/02.+EXP+Source+Systems+Mappings+for+return+and+reversals%3A+T=
ransactions+Details">02. EXP Source Systems Mappings for return and reversa=
ls: Transactions Details</a></span></span></li>
<li>Experience API- Source Systems Data Mapping: <a href=3D"/display/ARTC/A=
ccount+Experience+API-+Source+Systems+Mapping">Account Experience API- Sour=
ce Systems Mapping</a></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
