al-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image" draggable=3D"false" heigh=
t=3D"261" src=3D"0895aa2bd68c2ffc6e44adfcc3eeb582063b30b59cde7dbc1c00ef2ff5=
65edd4" data-image-src=3D"/download/attachments/1707781098/image-2025-4-14_=
11-33-51.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1772423298237&amp;api=3Dv2"=
 data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"2310644001"=
 data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment=
" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-2025-4-14_11-33-51.png" data-=
base-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au" data-linked-resource-con=
tent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1707781098" da=
ta-linked-resource-container-version=3D"41" alt=3D"" width=3D"468"></span><=
/p>
<p>Detail refers to the Jira&nbsp; <span class=3D"jira-issue resolved" data=
-jira-key=3D"ART-45830"> <a href=3D"https://jira.srv.westpac.com.au/browse/=
ART-45830" class=3D"jira-issue-key"><img class=3D"icon" src=3D"https://jira=
.srv.westpac.com.au:8444/secure/viewavatar?size=3Dxsmall&amp;avatarId=3D103=
00&amp;avatarType=3Dissuetype">ART-45830</a> - <span class=3D"summary">Tran=
saction listing source update to ATLAS &amp; display narratives in customer=
 &amp; staff portal</span> <span class=3D"aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle   =
          aui-lozenge-success
     jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">Done</span> </span></p>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-03.SD:TransactionDetails(CustomerPortal)-OperationalImpacts">O=
perational Impacts</h2>
<h3 id=3D"id-03.SD:TransactionDetails(CustomerPortal)-Logging"><span style=
=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Logging</span></h3>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">The recommended logging framework =
to use for API development is<span>&nbsp;</span></span><a class=3D"external=
-link" href=3D"http://www.slf4j.org/" rel=3D"nofollow">SLF4J</a><span style=
=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">, and it has<span>&nbsp;</span></span><a class=
=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/plugins/ser=
vlet/search?q=3Dproject%3AWDP+slf4j" rel=3D"nofollow">widest adoption</a><s=
pan style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><span>&nbsp;</span>across WDP platform =
APIs as of March 2020. You can read more here: <a href=3D"/display/WDPIPAAS=
/Logging+Framework+-+Java">Logging Framework - Java</a>.</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">As a general concern, we should ma=
sk any <strong><u>PII</u></strong> data or <u><strong>sensitive</strong> </=
u>identifiers.&nbsp;</span></p>
<h3 id=3D"id-03.SD:TransactionDetails(CustomerPortal)-Security"><span style=
=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Security</span></h3>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">In addition to client side data va=
lidation, server side validation should also be performed to ensure that th=
e correct request is being received from the UI. The&nbsp;<a class=3D"exter=
nal-link" href=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projects/UI-WWW1/rep=
os/wdp-ui-expcommon/browse/packages/bootstrap" rel=3D"nofollow">@wdpui/comm=
on-middleware</a><span>&nbsp;</span>package (part of @wdpui/common-bootstra=
p) provides some middleware to enhance the security of experience APIs. The=
 common bootstrap is required to be used in all projects unless an exemptio=
n is received from ISG. &nbsp;<a href=3D"/display/MESH/6.3.8+Security">6.3.=
8 Security</a></span></p>
<p><br></p>
